{No one has ever seen $0's face. This does not mean anyone even wishes to see her face.},
{After listening to $0's murmurs, one can assume that she is longing for someone.},
{It is best to leave her attached to the wall as it is. }
{I just hope that the employees have brought earplugs.}
]

[
{$0 always stands in the same pose. If it weren't for her babbling, one may well believe her to be a statue.},
{ #0 doesn't seem to worry much about $0, because she just stands there, no matter who enters the containment unit.},
{#0 seems okay around $0.},
{The wall around $0 is moldy, but no one cares to do anything about it.}
]

[
{While #0 is working, $0 lets out incomprehensible mumbles.},
{While #0 is working, the containment unit is silent. $0 breaks the silence by whispering frantically. },
{$0 doesn’t even twitch, but she seems to feel the presence of #0 in the containment unit. },
{Even though $0 has not moved, #0 finds her creepy.}
]

[
{The words are faint and muffled.},
{The whispering seems to be getting louder.},
{It almost seems like one could understand what is being said if only they concentrate harder, but of course, no employee dares to do so.},
{As always, the muffled whispers are incomprehensible and ignored by everyone.}
]

[
{#0 tries to concentrate on the task at hand.},
{#0 knows that ignoring her is the best choice.},
{#0 does not response to whatever $0 says, and pretends to be deaf.},
{#0 hurries to get the job done and to leave the room as soon as possible. }
